	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=86947><span id=Guru>Annheiser</span></a><br><b><span id=Guru>Guru</span></b><br><span id=notbold>170 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>You have to look at what kind of haste it is. Worn haste can not stack together. Your Velium Swiftblade is worn Haste so it will not stack with another worn haste item (like FBSS, CoF). If you want further haste, you'll need to either upgrade the swiftblade to a higher worn haste %, acquire an item that is clickable Haste, or have a partner that can give you song haste and/or spell haste.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br>**********************************<br>"<span style='color: red;'>Man who goes to bed with itchy bum, wakes with smelly fingers.</span style='color: red;'>"</td></td></tr>
